Hey guys, Rick here to explain the reel. The joke here starts off with your dad asking you what the opposite of ladyfingers is. Ladyfingers is a type of biscuit so you might think that the opposite of them is something that’s the opposite of a biscuit. However, after asking your dad what the answer is, he responds by saying “mentos.” This may sound super confusing at first because how are mentos (a type of candy) the exact opposite of lady fingers? The answer to this though is because the opposite of lady is men, and the opposite of fingers is toes. So when you put the definitions of the words inside you can see how mentos and ladyfingers are opposites!
